/ The items a multipage preview will skip, each with its contract reasons.
/ The list is capped in MultipagePreview (a sheet may hold thousands); the
/ batch count conveys the true scale, this names the first handful.
%ul.small.mb-0
  - preview.invalid_items.each do |item|
    %li
      %span.fw-semibold= item.label
      %ul.mb-0
        - item.errors.each do |err|
          %li= err
  - if preview.invalid_count > preview.invalid_items.size
    %li.text-muted= "…and #{preview.invalid_count - preview.invalid_items.size} more."
